{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"453-happy-and-sad-tell-me-now-series","title":"Happy and Sad (Tell me now series)","description":"Often, an inquisitive child asks his parents an endless set of questions. The 'Tell me ... now!' Series describes how interesting the questions and answers turn out. This one is about feelings and emotions.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Madhav Chavan"],"illustrators":["Rijuta Ghate"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/453-happy-and-sad-tell-me-now-series"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/722033/size3/6f953dea1448b109b24b70edf7350a65.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/722033/size6/6f953dea1448b109b24b70edf7350a65.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/5857/size6/f75d8aede52de9d7e99d2d9a0cd8eb3d.jpg","text":"Why is the baby crying?","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/5858/size6/b0e7cccf9cf4b199d606e8c88f720a8a.jpg","text":"I think she is hungry.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/5859/size6/fe4e86fb3fcfef1ff5c3cb238ad43ece.jpg","text":"Why is the boy sad?","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/5860/size6/ec03fb9673be2ce65fef206c87d53983.jpg","text":"I think he is missing his father.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/5861/size6/49b25024d60a439ad450c9d1b